---
import DevLayout from '../../../layouts/DevLayout.astro';
import ExampleAccordion from '../../../components/examples/ExampleAccordion.astro';
---

<DevLayout>
  <ExampleAccordion />
  <section class="component-info-section py-5">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="mb-3">Example Accordion Component</h2>
      <p>
        <strong>ExampleAccordion</strong> is a section component that demonstrates an interactive accordion with smooth animations. It supports both single (only one open at a time) and multiple (multiple can be open) accordion modes.
      </p>
      
      <div class="card mb-4">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3 class="h5 mb-3">Accordion Features</h3>
          <ul class="mb-0">
            <li>Follows BEM structure and project section conventions</li>
            <li>Section wrapper: <code>page-sec page-sec--example-accordion</code> with <code>container</code></li>
            <li>Two accordion types: single (default) and multiple (with <code>data-accordion="multiple"</code>)</li>
            <li>Smooth height animations with CSS transitions</li>
            <li>Accessible with proper focus states and keyboard navigation</li>
            <li>Visual indicators (arrows) that rotate when active</li>
            <li>Hover and active states with brand colors</li>
            <li>Fully responsive: mobile-first design</li>
            <li>All styles in dedicated SCSS partial, imported in <code>main.scss</code></li>
            <li>JavaScript functionality in dedicated module</li>
            <li>Ready for use in design system and real site pages</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card mb-4">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3 class="h5 mb-3">Usage Examples</h3>
          
          <h6 class="mt-3">Basic Single Accordion</h6>
          <pre style="background:#f8f8f8;padding:1rem;border-radius:6px;overflow:auto"><code>{`<div class="accordion js__example-accordion">
  <div class="accordion-item">
    <button class="accordion-header">
      Accordion Header
    </button>
    <div class="accordion-body">
      <div class="accordion-body__inner">
        Accordion content here
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>`}</code></pre>

          <h6 class="mt-3">Multiple Accordion (multiple can be open)</h6>
          <pre style="background:#f8f8f8;padding:1rem;border-radius:6px;overflow:auto"><code>{`<div class="accordion js__example-accordion" data-accordion="multiple">
  <div class="accordion-item">
    <button class="accordion-header">
      Accordion Header
    </button>
    <div class="accordion-body">
      <div class="accordion-body__inner">
        Accordion content here
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>`}</code></pre>

          <h6 class="mt-3">Component Usage</h6>
          <pre style="background:#f8f8f8;padding:1rem;border-radius:6px;overflow:auto"><code>{`---
import ExampleAccordion from '../../../components/examples/ExampleAccordion.astro';
---
<ExampleAccordion />`}</code></pre>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3 class="h5 mb-3">Technical Details</h3>
          <ul class="mb-0">
            <li><strong>CSS Classes:</strong> Uses <code>js__example-accordion</code> for JavaScript targeting</li>
            <li><strong>Animation:</strong> 300ms height transition with smooth easing</li>
            <li><strong>Accessibility:</strong> Proper focus states, semantic HTML, and keyboard navigation</li>
            <li><strong>JavaScript:</strong> Module-based initialization with event delegation</li>
            <li><strong>Responsive:</strong> Adapts padding and font sizes for mobile devices</li>
            <li><strong>Brand Colors:</strong> Uses brand blue (#0099f7) for active states</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</DevLayout> 